Hom_{AbX}(Z,F) isomorphic to F
\mathsf{Ab} \to \mathsf{PSh}(X)
A \mapsto (U \mapsto A)
\mathsf{Ab} \to \mathsf{Sh}(X)
A \mapsto \underline{A}
\mathbb{Z} \in \mathsf{Ab}
\mathsf{Ab} \to \mathsf{Set}
\underline{\hom}(\underline{\mathbb{Z}},F)
U \mapsto \hom(\underline{\mathbb{Z}}|_U,F|_U)
\hom(\underline{\mathbb{Z}}|_U,F|_U) \stackrel{2.}{\cong} \hom(\mathbb{Z},\Gamma(U,F)) \stackrel{3.}{\cong} \Gamma(U,F)
